If you are a spellcaster ([[bard]], [[cleric]], [[druid]], or bearer of the [[Mark of Healing]]), this staff allows you to cast [[cure wounds]] and [[restoration]] using your own power. You also gain one additional spellcasting [[stress]] box which you can only use to cast these spells.
